{"tid":2326890,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★滙豐及渣打銀行2016年共聘用六百多名中共黨員","createTime":"2020-12-15T15:48:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-15T16:04:52.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"bce606804d8b54cdcc21dde23305dab105d8ccac","tid":2326890,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T15:48:28.000Z","msg":"名單涉及195萬名中共黨員資料，包括姓名、職位、地址、電話，顯示他們已滲透眾多跨國企業大學及外交機關等。包括英國、美國、澳洲等十國駐上海的領事館，當中涉及的英國領事館員工工作地點跟軍情六處小組近在咫尺。經中國國營人力資源公司的黨支部僱用，據稱有至少二百幾名中共黨員為過百家上海的外國機構工作。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\">滙豐及渣打銀行2016年共聘用六百多中共黨員</span></strong>；多間國防企業，如波音、空中巴士、勞斯萊斯及大藥廠如輝瑞、阿斯利康、葛蘭素史克等，均僱用數以百計的中共黨員。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=416707\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D416707&d=ZAqn3h4t0e4XfOyVRCtvGFgnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=8f2243e2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D416707&h=b8aecde9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=416707</a>"},{"pid":"7bdb6a83610aca09db22614d0e1f8d34968b31ab","tid":2326890,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T15:48:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13f52d24097bdcae609a9d2e20aa96beb62b8108","tid":2326890,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T15:49:15.000Z","msg":"not a news"},{"pid":"407dfd8d52cbb703522f377c2650aa48f9969dc3","tid":2326890,"uid":170335,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"